com.umbrella.umbrella

Class CourseSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.umbrella.umbrella.CourseSet

  • public class CourseSet
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by wauch on 2018-02-20. A hashmap of courses with various operations that can be performed on it as a set. Used as an entity for use cases such as the student's list of courses.
